{"tid":1110151,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"喺香港做 IT 狗有咩意義？","createTime":"2019-04-16T12:34:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-25T13:21:26.000Z","uid":125976,"like":34,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2d10a1c1a1cf0fba76c1fbf1d8a8a9b7440bd7c8","tid":1110151,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T12:34:38.000Z","msg":"唔明點解咁多人想入行做 IT<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>做 IN HOUSE</strong><br />\n幫啲港資大公司 main 住啲十幾年前嘅舊 system<br />\nMain 得好冇多謝你<br />\n俾你 Revamp 到煥然一新又點？<br />\n有咩事第一個屌你 IT<br />\n炒人第一個炒你 IT<br />\n求撚其俾部 4：3 mon + N 年前舊機你<br />\n你就日日改 Business Logic 改撚到隻屄咁<br />\n好人好者。。。走去幫人做狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>做 VENDOR</strong><br />\n唔理你做 CP, GT 定其他 Software House<br />\n你日日 OT 都係為咗幫公司 chur projects<br />\n但有冇諗過間公司唔係屬於你<br />\n啲 Project References 都唔係屬於你<br />\n你只係公司請返嚟嘅一名撚狗<br />\n做得好唔會有股份分<br />\n做得慢俾人屌鑊金<br />\n好人好者。。。走去幫人做狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>做 STARTUP</strong><br />\n做 Banker 二世祖老細拍吓政府膊頭就攞到三幾球<br />\n人哋吹吓水就話搞個「萬能 App」<br />\n問題係邊個落手「搞」先？<br />\n咪攞嚿錢求其出兩三皮請你班撚狗搞囉<br />\n你日日改撚到隻屄咁<br />\n二世祖老細每日都想加啲「新功能」<br />\n經過你哋無數次 Revamp &amp; Re-design<br />\n嚿嘢終於出街<br />\n但嚿嘢唔屬於你<br />\n二世祖老細 cap 夠水玩撚夠<br />\n就炒晒你班撚狗<br />\n好人好者。。。走去幫人做狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>結論</strong><br />\n講真，係人都知 IT 唔係咁「搞」<br />\n所以叻 / 有家底嗰班「IT人」一早走撚晒外國啦<br />\n剩返低嗰啲。。。<br />\n咪留喺香港 / 大陸做狗囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nRef: <a href=\"https://github.com/996icu/996.ICU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2F996icu%2F996.ICU&d=gujWeq0O8VISlzAOvjwOFoeNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=5d7a925b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/996icu/996.ICU</a>"},{"pid":"64bf782b3130bf9b40a9463c3e4f83aef6e43831","tid":1110151,"uid":76747,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T12:36:13.000Z","msg":"全城講緊安心,理撚得你做唔做IT"},{"pid":"ff38d5731ffac5b691e73a540f7d6000b9c106c2","tid":1110151,"uid":9769,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T12:37:51.000Z","msg":"你下個星期先出Post吧，今日無人有興趣想聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a03917792d2e82194e17f0d2b8693ae988c99a3","tid":1110151,"uid":125976,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"64bf782b3130bf9b40a9463c3e4f83aef6e43831","tid":1110151,"uid":76747,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T12:36:13.000Z","msg":"全城講緊安心,理撚得你做唔做IT"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T12:38:31.000Z","msg":"人哋啲「私人活動」關你乜事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"984dfffad1b1b978a16e6b2a634063590231a3d8","tid":1110151,"uid":9769,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T12:40:39.000Z","msg":"繼續努力啦，做Tech最緊要你既Tech夠勁，然後學做人，之後等機會黎。"},{"pid":"1be31ea3becf94f59ca05a5211aee8e71fa21b0a","tid":1110151,"uid":64172,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"984dfffad1b1b978a16e6b2a634063590231a3d8","tid":1110151,"uid":9769,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T12:40:39.000Z","msg":"繼續努力啦，做Tech最緊要你既Tech夠勁，然後學做人，之後等機會黎。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T13:44:09.000Z","msg":"你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d90b5ebd82798811837208d0ce74b6dc884d1181","tid":1110151,"uid":210688,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1be31ea3becf94f59ca05a5211aee8e71fa21b0a","tid":1110151,"uid":64172,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"984dfffad1b1b978a16e6b2a634063590231a3d8","tid":1110151,"uid":9769,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T12:40:39.000Z","msg":"繼續努力啦，做Tech最緊要你既Tech夠勁，然後學做人，之後等機會黎。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16